videos.headline: Keyontae Johnson drains a 3
videos.description: Keyontae Johnson starts things off hot for Kansas State with a 3-pointer.

videos.headline: Desi Sills gets the steal and the basket
videos.description: Desi Sills grabs the steal and the layup for the Wildcats.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Desi Sills gets the steal and the basket) 2023/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Joseph Yesufu drains the 3
videos.description: Dajuan Harris dishes to Joseph Yesufu for a Kansas 3-pointer.

videos.headline: Gradey Dick slams huge dunk for Kansas
videos.description: Gradey Dick hits a powerful one-handed slam for Kansas.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Gradey Dick slams huge dunk for Kansas) 2023/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Desi Sills knocks down 3-pointer for Kansas State
videos.description: Desi Sills hits a 3 to increase Kansas State's lead over Kansas.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Desi Sills knocks down 3-pointer for Kansas State) 2023/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Keyontae Johnson dances after layup
videos.description: Keyontae Johnson shows off his moves after driving to the hoop for a layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Keyontae Johnson dances after layup) 2023/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Markquis Nowell steals and scores to put KSU up late
videos.description: Markquis Nowell scores off a steal to give Kansas State a late lead over Kansas.

videos.headline: Jalen Wilson reaches career-high 36 points with 3-pointer
videos.description: Kansas' Jalen Wilson hits a new career high in points with a 3-pointer against Kansas State in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jalen Wilson reaches career-high 36 points with 3-pointer) 2023/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kansas State takes down rival Kansas in hectic OT finish
videos.description: Keyontae Johnson puts Kansas State ahead in overtime with a slam dunk and the fans storm the court as the Wildcats upset No. 2 Kansas.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_Highlight (Kansas State takes down rival Kansas in hectic OT finish) 2023/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bill Self's poorly timed timeout cancels out Jalen Wilson's 3
videos.description: Bill Self calls timeout moments before Jalen Wilson takes a 3-pointer, calling off the shot.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bill Self's poorly timed timeout cancels out Jalen Wilson's 3) 2023/01/18 ESHEET
